 partners and strive to keep them informed and up to date regarding the progress of their loans we provide our brokers with competitive compensation learn more imh strives to maintain transparency and trust with its investors our commitment to our shareholders drives imh to be the best in its class and build a strong reputation for honesty and integrity these are among our most valuable assets   the shareholder portal allows our investors to create a personal account granting access to the latest in shareholder news and enabling them to manage the details of their account access the shareholder portal login now imh financial corporation quotes  news  google financecookies help us deliver our services by using our services you agree to our use of cookieslearn moregot itmy accountsearchmapsyoutubeplaynewsgmaildrivecalendargoogletranslatephotosmoreshoppingwalletfinancedocsbooksbloggercontactshangoutskeepeven more from googlesign inhidden fieldssearch financeadobe flash player is required for interactive charts allowfinanceimh financial corporationcompanysummarynewsrelated companiesmarketsnewsportfoliosstock screenergoogle domestic trendsrecent quotes  daysyou have no recent quoteschg   imh financial corporation   officers and directors william meris ceo jim abood senior vice president and corporate secretary ryan muranaka senior vice president underwriting address  n scottsdale rd paradise valley az usa  phone website links wwwimhrecom imh financial deals in real estate lending and investment mainly in the southwestern us although its family of companies historically have focused on acquiring and originating shortterm bridge loans to enable commercial real estate development and construction market conditions  mainly lack of mortgage capital availability  are prompting the company to change course its focus now is to make investments across a more diverse set of target assets including interim loans used to pay off construction or property loans and whole commercial re