lection workout and sale of new and legacy loans and reo assets including financing of such asset sales commercial real estate leasing operations which consists of a commercial medical office building located in stafford texas and corporate and other which consists of the companys centralized general and administrative corporate treasury and deposit gathering activities and interest expense associated with debt issuancesthe companys focus is to invest in originate manage and dispose of commercial real estate mortgage and related investments it also focuses to perform functions related thereto including developing managing and either holding for investment or disposing of real property acquired through foreclosure investment or other meansas of december   the companys loan portfolio consisted of nine first mortgage loans of its nine outstanding loans as of december   the company had three performing loans » full overview of ipoifcn company address imh financial corp  n scottsdale rd ste scottsdale   az    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation lawrence bain  samuel montes  jonathan brohard  greg hanss  ryan muranaka  » more officers  directors imh financial corp news briefimh financial files for nontimely k apr   » more ipoifcn news related topics stocksstock screenerfinancialsconsumer lending